Do you love opening new tabs but hate the same old boring page that shows up every time? Well, have no fear, because we've got the solution for you! Introducing our extension that'll have you laughing so hard, you might just forget why you opened the tab in the first place.

Every. Single. Time. you open a new tab, you'll be hit with a brand spankin' new dad joke. Yes, you heard that right. No more staring at a blank page or mindlessly scrolling through social media feeds. With our extension, you'll get a guaranteed chuckle every time you open a new tab. It's like having a personal comedian at your fingertips!

And let's be real, who doesn't need a good laugh these days? Life can be tough, but at least you'll have a reason to smile every time you open a new tab. So go ahead and install our extension, and let the good times roll. Trust us, there's nothing better than a dad joke to brighten up your day.
